    <p>The Ber­satu sec­re­tary-gen­eral was a ju­nior min­is­ter in Umno un­til its elec­tion de­feat in 2018, af­ter which he de­fected to Ber­satu.</p>
    <p>He, too, helped to block Mr An­war’s as­cent to the top job in Fe­bru­ary. As the min­is­ter in charge of se­cu­rity, he was a key player in the bid to de­clare an emer­gency.</p>

